Package: libcamera0.7-qbcfork
Architecture: arm64 armhf
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 libcamera-ipa-qbcfork (= ${binary:Version}),
 libpisp1 (>= 1.5.0),
Conflicts:
 libcamera0,
 libcamera0.6,
 libcamera0.7,
Replaces:
 libcamera0,
 libcamera0.6,
 libcamera0.7,
Provides:
 libcamera0.7 (= 0.7.1),
Description: Complex camera support library (IMX294 QBC + IMX585 ClearHDR fork)
 Fork of libcamera carrying an IMX294 quad-Bayer (QBC) software remosaic
 in the PiSP pipeline handler plus IMX585 ClearHDR support (CCMP unwrap,
 per-channel BLC, software stats for high-bit-depth raw paths). Pairs
 with rpicam-apps-qbcfork.
 .
 This binary package contains the libcamera and libcamera-base shared
 libraries.

Package: libcamera-ipa-qbcfork
Architecture: arm64 armhf
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Conflicts:
 libcamera-ipa,
Replaces:
 libcamera-ipa,
Provides:
 libcamera-ipa (= ${binary:Version}),
Description: Complex camera support library - IPA modules (QBC fork)
 IPA (Image Processing Algorithm) modules for the libcamera-qbcfork
 build, including the rpi/vc4 and rpi/pisp IPAs with fork-specific
 tuning for IMX294 QBC and IMX585 ClearHDR. Ships the libcamera data
 tree (tuning JSONs, signed IPA proxy helper) under /usr/share and
 /usr/libexec.

Package: libcamera-v4l2-qbcfork
Architecture: arm64 armhf
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
 libcamera0.7-qbcfork (= ${binary:Version}),
Conflicts:
 libcamera-v4l2,
 libcamera-tools,
Replaces:
 libcamera-v4l2,
 libcamera-tools,
Provides:
 libcamera-v4l2 (= ${binary:Version}),
 libcamera-tools (= ${binary:Version}),
Description: Complex camera support library - V4L2 compatibility shim (QBC fork)
 V4L2 compatibility layer (v4l2-compat.so) that lets legacy V4L2
 applications consume libcamera cameras, plus the libcamerify wrapper
 helper. Also takes over the upstream libcamera-tools package slot
 since this fork builds without the qcam / cam / lc-compliance binaries
 to keep the install footprint small.

