Provides:
 python3-libcamera (= ${binary:Version}),
Description: Complex camera support library - Python bindings (QBC fork)
 Python 3 bindings for the libcamera-qbcfork shared library, built
 against the same libcamera 0.7.x ABI as the upstream python3-libcamera
 package. Required by picamera2 when the QBC fork is the installed
 libcamera stack.

